Description.SourceString: The main objective of the game is to build teams of Heroes and conquer territory on the world map. In order to succeed, you'll need to upgrade the level and stats of your Heroes, create teams to tackle different challenges, and upgrade your Headquarters (and other buildings) to increase your power.
